{"type": "article", "id": 38364, "title": "睡不着觉？这里有个陪你呼吸的机器人｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-02T23:25:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 38175, "name": "Thirst"}, {"id": 38176, "name": "Commonwealth Brewing"}, {"id": 38177, "name": "Chialing Chang"}, {"id": 38178, "name": "Jordan Bolton"}, {"id": 38179, "name": "Rafael Vangelis"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 134, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170302222328ZRlhJ5vUoBfMHTyL.jpg", "contents": "<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Somnox by TU Delft</h3><p>无需服用安眠药，只要抱着柔软的枕头就能入睡或许不再是天方夜谭了。有研究表明，呼吸是影响睡眠质量的一大要素，而缓慢、有规律的呼吸节奏可以帮助人们尽快入睡。基于这个发现，来自代尔夫特理工大学（TU Delft）的团队在荷兰设计周上揭晓了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.somnox.nl/\">Somnox</a> 的枕头机器人。像是一颗大花生的 Somnox 内置了数个用于收集睡眠情况的传感器，人工智能算法会根据这些信息为用户量身定制呼吸节奏，再由枕头将这一稳定的节奏模拟出来。随着用户的呼吸慢慢和 Somnox 的节奏趋于一致，失眠的症状就能得到有效的缓解。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222415pxK3uVThYLUzodRD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222415opM73RAO8BUiYZsq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222415dUOj8m2Bt39EMFxw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Selah Pad by Selah Design</h3><p>虽然市面上有各式各样的鼠标垫，但把它们和苹果的 Magic Mouse 放在一块儿总有一种微妙的违和感。为了填补这一空缺，美国一支名为 Selah Design 的设计团队历时两年时间研发了一款同名的鼠标垫。和其他鼠标垫相比，白色的 Selah Pad 因为优雅的外观就加分不少。除此之外，它的表面采用了更符合人体工学的起伏设计，能让手腕关节处于自然的舒展位置。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/selahdesign/the-selah-pad-for-apple-mouse\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 15 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222433uF3pOXmEG4cRLT5Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703022224333y2MiYZ1hlKf7uCI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.888235\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222433mZ1LKGhdyesrF5Vv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.598529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Poster by Jordan Bolton</h3><p>热爱电影的英国摄影师 Jordan Bolton 以制作道具和布景主题的电影海报见长。在反复观看一部电影后，他会亲手制作出微缩道具和场景模型，再耐心地将它们像标本一样整齐排列，采取俯拍的角度拍摄下来。最近，Bolton 以吉卜力推出的动画电影为灵感，一改原本多元的材料选择，而是利用柔软的橡皮泥还原出电影中的物品。如果你对这种风格感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/uk/shop/JordanBoltonDesign\">链接</a>购买，售价从 8.84 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222453sp9JgZ72I3jAVuh6.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.423810\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222453fiqAkuMcTPnlezHN.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.407619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017030222245391fWHyFeiKBZoOvp.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.410476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222453yWSNm3hUCDsMJ0xq.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.426667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Second Nature by Chialing Chang</h3><p>在制作家具的过程中，天然的木料通常被加工成干净的束状或板状，剩下的树皮和边材则被当作废料处理——而在台湾设计师 <a href=\"http://chialingchang.com/\">Chialing Chang</a> 看来，这些木料固有的元素也可以成为家具的亮点。这套让人联想到树干的 <a href=\"http://chialingchang.com/Second_Nature/\">Second Nature</a> 家具系列就是 Chang 亲手挑选出一批废弃木料，再将它们像积木一样组合而成的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222513akLd6v9l51tVAoBx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703022225132PwJkWCprDLcdMe0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703022225135KvsywIYiDxBcnCN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222513KfODkaBL758cS6QI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222516vtMJrGuDQE1K49OA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222516X1Dq4ICEla9rZLjW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Commonwealth Brewing Co. by Thirst</h3><p>看着这些颜色斑斓的罐头，你能猜到它们分别对应了怎样的风味吗？当美国精酿啤酒厂 <a href=\"http://www.commonwealthbrewingcompany.com/\">Commonwealth Brewing Co.</a> 委托创意机构 <a href=\"http://thirstcraft.com/\">Thirst</a> 进行包装设计时，负责人 Jeramy Biggie 表示他们希望顾客能从罐头上看到它的味道。为了实现这种效果，设计师将不同的油、醋、以及墨水混合在一起，再用镜头捕捉下了它们不断融合时产生的特殊纹理，看上去就像是刚晃动完啤酒一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222528uyDlIXwasBEHbJn3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222529UBVSgvtHzM0JIR92.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222529aDXVAOs8utG7lI0n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302222529BKgTFRneJdP7OIQc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703022225291gdPv3Zq2xRFLziB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.678667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Analogue Loaders by Rafael Vangelis</h3><p><a href=\"http://raphaelvangelis.com/\">Rafael Vangelis</a> 是一名现居英国伦敦的动画导演，在新作 Analogue Loaders 中，他通过定格动画和传统动画的结合，将生活中常见的粘土、木材，甚至是鸡蛋打造成了 3D 版的加载动画。假如转轮和进度条都变成这种有趣的形式，漫长的等待似乎变得不那么难以忍受了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/203671501\">链接</a>观看到完整的短片，Vangelis 还上传了它的<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/201632751\">幕后花絮</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170302223114jAtManC6RZWHe9Kg.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.558333\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703022226055Ma7OpFoC9fg8V1y.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703022226052NFmKo8w0EzPi3s9.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div>"}